        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "The Setup",
          "description": "Removes all Burn status effects (including Mega Healing Burn) from enemy units on the battlefield. The user is granted a Charge, Super Stealth, and a Stealth Shield.\n\nThen grants all enemies the Mega Poison status effect for 200TU. This will overwrite other status effects on those units.\n\nThen steals up to 2 Spirit from the enemy team for each Poisoned enemy on the battlefield.\n\nUsable if the user does not have the Stealth status effect. If this skill is used 3 times within 10TU, it becomes locked for 50TU.\n\nMega Poison deals 20 times the damage of normal Poison and cannot be overwritten by normal Poison or Super Poison. Certain skills are affected by and may consume charges. A unit can store a maximum of 3 charges.",
