      "SingleAttackALupinRegular": {
        "id": "SingleAttackALupinRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Sneaky Shot",
          "description": "500% damage to 1 enemy, and the user is granted a Charge. Heals the user for 100% of total damage dealt. This attack ignores Guardians, any enemy status effects, damage reduction effects, revenge passive skills, and skin passive skills. Damage from this attack does not wake up sleeping enemies.\n\nThe user steals all Sleep Wards, Stun Wards, Poison Wards, and Instant Death Wards from the hit target even if they are defeated by this attack. Then the user has their current TU reduced by 10TU for each type of ward stolen. Usable if the user has Stealth or if The Setup is locked.\n\nEach Ward prevents their named effect from being applied once, then is removed. Identical Wards cannot stack. An Instant Death Ward prevents this unit from being immediately defeated without damage by a non-boss enemy once, then is removed. Instant Death Wards cannot be ignored and cannot stack. Stolen wards will still be removed from the target even if the user already had them.",
          "selected": "500% damage, May Steal Wards & Reduce TU"
